description:
Quinn Sullivan - Cyclone (2011) FLAC

Cyclone is the debut album from the New Bedford, Massachusetts 14-year-old talent. Sullivan began playing the guitar at 3, and his remarkable ability came to national attention at 6, when Ellen DeGeneres, who often showcases child prodigies, invited him to play on her show. But his career did not truly take off until 2009, when Mr. Guy, the Chicago bluesman, invited him on tour after meeting him backstage at a show.
